'''[[Peru]]''' is a signatory to the [[Berne Convention]], and the basic law on [[copyright]] is contained in ''Legislative Decree No. 822 of April 23, 1996''. Related and subsequent amending legislation are listed at the relevant WIPO page.<ref>[http://www.wipo.int/wipolex/en/details.jsp?id=3412 Peru.] [[WIPO]], 2013. Retrieved 4 August 2013.</ref>

